# ── Anthropic API Key ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Required for Tamil translation (EN→TA) using Claude Haiku.
# Without this, the system falls back to Google Translate (needs internet)
# or argostranslate (offline but lower quality).
#
# Get your key at: https://console.anthropic.com/
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# ── Ollama settings (optional overrides) ────────────────────────────────────
# Default: http://localhost:11434
# OLLAMA_BASE_URL=http://localhost:11434
#
# Model is AUTO-SELECTED from what you have installed.
# Recommended for Tamil: ollama pull llama3.1:8b
# Good fallback:         ollama pull mistral
